lead_paragraph: The Exceutive Committee of the Philadelphia Independent Consolidation Party withdrew their ticket Inst night. The Whig, Democratic, and Na. tive tickets are now in the field. There were 138 deaths in Philadolphia last week: adults, 67; children, 76: of Consumption, 17; Dysentery, 15.
